01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.585
=Episode 24=

01:51.760 --> 01:52.480
(Yan Studio)
Granny!

01:54.200 --> 01:55.840
You're so happy today.

01:56.320 --> 01:58.239
Got good news

01:58.359 --> 01:59.999
to share with me?

02:00.279 --> 02:01.120
Look at our outfits.

02:01.400 --> 02:01.999
Pretty, right?

02:02.840 --> 02:04.320
We made them ourselves.

02:04.519 --> 02:05.999
Grandma, take a closer look.

02:06.320 --> 02:07.439
Every stitch

02:07.519 --> 02:10.040
is pure handwork.

02:10.079 --> 02:10.959
You must know this.

02:11.280 --> 02:13.519
Every single stitch represents
our intangible heritage.

02:13.679 --> 02:14.200
Grandma.

02:14.399 --> 02:15.280
- Look.
- The entire outfit.

02:15.280 --> 02:16.880
Doesn't Lin look like a model?

02:17.239 --> 02:17.799
Pretty, right?

02:18.760 --> 02:19.519
Like a model, huh?

02:20.359 --> 02:21.600
Let me show you Yan's outfit.

02:21.679 --> 02:22.440
Look at me.

02:22.839 --> 02:24.600
- Is that pretty?
- You look great, really.

02:25.040 --> 02:26.320
Let me get you closer.

02:26.440 --> 02:27.160
Look at her.

02:27.280 --> 02:28.959
Does she look like a businesswoman?

02:30.040 --> 02:31.119
- What do you think?
- Absolutely!

02:31.119 --> 02:31.799
Look closer.

02:31.959 --> 02:33.280
We made all of this ourselves.

02:33.399 --> 02:34.000
Look.

02:34.000 --> 02:34.704
Gorgeous, right?

02:35.359 --> 02:36.200
What do you think?

02:36.399 --> 02:37.839
Lovely! So lovely!

02:38.119 --> 02:39.600
When you wear this,

02:40.160 --> 02:42.600
you just look like a little fairy!

02:43.320 --> 02:44.720
Then you're the fairy queen!

02:44.720 --> 02:45.440
- Right?
- Yes!

02:45.480 --> 02:46.519
You're the most pretty,

02:46.519 --> 02:47.760
the most lovely fairy queen!

02:48.280 --> 02:48.920
By the way,

02:49.359 --> 02:51.760
we made a custom set just for you.

02:51.959 --> 02:53.000
We'll bring it to you.

02:53.200 --> 02:55.040
If I wear clothes

02:55.239 --> 02:56.679
made by you girls,

02:56.799 --> 02:59.440
then I'll "look cute"!

02:59.959 --> 03:00.559
Grandma.

03:00.600 --> 03:01.920
You've been on your phone a lot!

03:02.160 --> 03:03.679
You even know "look cute" now.

03:04.440 --> 03:05.799
But that's not popular anymore.

03:06.639 --> 03:10.160
I am Yan Studio's

03:10.760 --> 03:12.399
number one superfan!

03:12.600 --> 03:14.320
You also know that?

03:15.408 --> 03:16.688
Watched many live streams too.

03:18.519 --> 03:19.040
Alright.

03:19.639 --> 03:21.399
Next time

03:21.799 --> 03:22.679
when you take photos,

03:22.679 --> 03:23.959
send me more, okay?

03:24.112 --> 03:24.839
Okay.

03:24.920 --> 03:26.000
Got it.

03:26.320 --> 03:26.959
Okay.

03:27.160 --> 03:28.200
We'll hang up now.

03:28.200 --> 03:28.839
Goodbye!

03:29.720 --> 03:30.399
Bye!

03:31.760 --> 03:33.239
Don't you feel so happy

03:33.239 --> 03:34.280
after every call with her?

03:34.799 --> 03:36.440
She's always smiling,

03:36.600 --> 03:38.040
supporting, and encouraging us.

03:40.480 --> 03:41.160
It's so nice.

03:43.639 --> 03:45.040
And she always

03:46.399 --> 03:47.720
picks up on the very first ring.

03:48.839 --> 03:49.559
So

03:50.160 --> 03:52.519
she is always waiting for us to call.

03:54.839 --> 03:55.440
That's true.

03:59.200 --> 04:01.440
I asked her to come to Jingzhou,

04:02.320 --> 04:03.440
but she refused.

04:04.480 --> 04:05.480
I can tell

04:06.959 --> 04:08.280
she's afraid

04:08.320 --> 04:09.600
she'll disturb our work

04:10.119 --> 04:11.359
or add to our burden.

04:15.679 --> 04:16.400
So...

04:18.359 --> 04:20.040
Yan Studio must succeed.

04:22.400 --> 04:23.559
We'll build

04:24.999 --> 04:26.480
our own home in Jingzhou

04:28.199 --> 04:29.400
so we can bring Grandma here

04:30.239 --> 04:31.400
to live with us.

04:33.160 --> 04:36.559
She can be at peace.

04:37.600 --> 04:38.679
We can make it.

04:43.280 --> 04:44.679
Careful, don't snag the fabric.

04:45.199 --> 04:46.640
- Be careful.
- I'm being careful.

04:47.319 --> 04:48.119
I'm even holding it.

04:48.119 --> 04:48.799
Hurry up.

04:48.960 --> 04:49.840
Take it off.

04:50.040 --> 04:51.199
Watch the gauze.

04:51.239 --> 04:52.112
Spread your arms out.

04:52.319 --> 04:53.040
Like this?

04:53.040 --> 04:53.712
Exactly.

04:53.840 --> 04:55.319
Otherwise, it'll tear.

04:55.952 --> 04:58.416
This afternoon I'll go fetch the goods.
Call me if anything.

05:08.480 --> 05:09.200
Hello?

05:09.920 --> 05:11.239
Our truck broke down on the road.

05:11.920 --> 05:13.080
What?

05:13.359 --> 05:14.480
Are you okay?

05:14.759 --> 05:15.439
I'm fine.

05:16.720 --> 05:18.999
But if this batch can't be
put in storage on time,

05:19.359 --> 05:21.239
