05:21.999 --> 05:24.799
And we have to pay heavy late fees.

05:25.759 --> 05:26.480
I called for help.

05:26.480 --> 05:28.520
They'll arrive
after three to four hours.

05:28.520 --> 05:29.040
So...

05:29.640 --> 05:30.799
I sent you my location.

05:31.080 --> 05:32.119
Send a truck here now.

05:32.359 --> 05:32.920
Okay.

05:33.328 --> 05:33.960
