05:34.040 --> 05:35.600
Should I ask Lin and Guan to go?

05:36.600 --> 05:37.168
No need.

05:37.400 --> 05:38.359
Stay at the office.

05:38.439 --> 05:39.520
For emergencies.

05:39.520 --> 05:40.119
Understood.

05:40.119 --> 05:41.600
Take care of yourself.

05:42.400 --> 05:43.239
Hurry up.

05:47.199 --> 05:47.728
Yao.

05:48.679 --> 05:49.400
Mr. Shen?

05:49.960 --> 05:50.879
You look panicked.

05:50.879 --> 05:51.879
Did something happen?

05:52.080 --> 05:53.160
Yan's in trouble.

05:55.439 --> 05:57.160
The truck broke down on the road.

06:34.160 --> 06:35.720
You... Why are you here?

06:35.720 --> 06:37.319
I'll move the goods. Get in the truck.

06:38.119 --> 06:38.799
I'll help you.

06:38.799 --> 06:39.559
It's okay.

06:39.999 --> 06:40.920
We can handle it.

06:40.960 --> 06:41.879
Come here.

06:41.999 --> 06:42.720
We'll finish soon.

06:42.759 --> 06:43.319
Come on.

06:49.400 --> 06:50.040
Be careful.

06:53.359 --> 06:53.999
We'll be quick.

06:54.439 --> 06:55.040
Wait.

06:55.679 --> 06:56.359
Hold this for me.

07:00.280 --> 07:00.840
Sir?

07:01.640 --> 07:02.080
Sir.

07:02.512 --> 07:03.280
Okay.

07:06.768 --> 07:09.755
â™ªSo simpleâ™ª

07:10.224 --> 07:12.641
â™ªIn the crowdâ™ª

07:14.313 --> 07:17.840
â™ªCan't see the future nowâ™ª

07:21.648 --> 07:24.336
â™ªYour toughness, your innocenceâ™ª

07:24.560 --> 07:27.440
â™ªHow can I lean on you? Yet not let goâ™ª

