07:38.480 --> 07:40.628
â™ªThat momentâ™ª

07:40.784 --> 07:43.184
â™ªI knew loveâ™ª

07:43.184 --> 07:45.680
â™ªYou're my oneâ™ª

07:45.680 --> 07:48.432
â™ªI realize when I lose youâ™ª

07:48.432 --> 07:51.472
â™ªThe more I let goâ™ª

07:51.472 --> 07:54.992
â™ªThe more it hurtsâ™ª

07:54.992 --> 07:57.072
â™ªI was the oneâ™ª

07:57.072 --> 07:59.824
â™ªWho chose to walk awayâ™ª

07:59.824 --> 08:02.831
â™ªIf given another chanceâ™ª

08:02.831 --> 08:05.679
â™ªLife's unwritten spaceâ™ª

08:05.679 --> 08:06.960
(Did Shen Haoming arrive?)

08:07.239 --> 08:08.759
(He offered to come himself.)

08:09.296 --> 08:11.590
â™ªFirst time I confessâ™ª

08:11.590 --> 08:14.270
â™ªI'm so ordinaryâ™ª

08:14.270 --> 08:16.896
â™ªLonging to earnâ™ª

08:16.896 --> 08:19.901
â™ªYour trust wholeâ™ª

08:19.901 --> 08:22.740
â™ªOne last look backâ™ª

08:22.740 --> 08:25.640
â™ªSay goodnight againâ™ª

08:25.640 --> 08:30.096
â™ªLaugh unrestrainedâ™ª

08:32.144 --> 08:34.138
â™ªTrue loveâ™ª

08:34.138 --> 08:36.944
â™ªI see it nowâ™ª

08:36.944 --> 08:39.784
â™ªYou've longâ™ª

08:39.784 --> 08:43.181
â™ªLived in my heartâ™ª

08:43.181 --> 08:45.767
â™ªAdmit lonelinessâ™ª

08:45.767 --> 08:48.449
â™ªWaiting for you to returnâ™ª

08:48.449 --> 08:51.258
â™ªThe happiness I oweâ™ª

08:51.258 --> 08:53.904
â™ªI'll repay you tomorrowâ™ª

08:53.904 --> 08:54.842
â™ªOhâ™ª

08:54.842 --> 08:57.129
â™ªYou're my oneâ™ª

08:58.199 --> 08:58.959
How many left?

09:02.000 --> 09:02.832
Almost done.

09:02.832 --> 09:06.288
â™ªThe more it hurtsâ™ª

09:06.288 --> 09:08.501
â™ªI was the oneâ™ª

09:08.501 --> 09:11.408
â™ªWho chose to walk awayâ™ª

09:11.408 --> 09:14.032
â™ªIf given another chanceâ™ª

09:14.032 --> 09:17.252
â™ªLife's unwritten spaceâ™ª

09:17.252 --> 09:21.368
â™ªNow I anticipateâ™ª

09:32.176 --> 09:34.389
â™ªNow I anticipateâ™ª

09:34.768 --> 09:38.035
â™ªA future with you in itâ™ª

09:42.079 --> 09:43.199
- Be careful.
- Let me help.

09:47.120 --> 09:47.880
Have some water.

09:48.240 --> 09:48.799
Thanks.

09:58.640 --> 09:59.280
Want more?

09:59.600 --> 10:00.319
No.

10:03.000 --> 10:04.439
You have plenty of staff.

10:04.799 --> 10:05.920
