10:08.880 --> 10:09.839
It's our first batch.

10:10.599 --> 10:11.839
I don't want any mishaps.

10:11.880 --> 10:12.559
So

10:13.199 --> 10:14.559
I came to check.

10:14.679 --> 10:16.479
I need to check the next batch.

10:19.520 --> 10:20.120
What about you?

10:21.360 --> 10:23.079
Got such a huge company,

10:23.920 --> 10:24.959
and you came yourself?

10:28.912 --> 10:30.000
There's a company retreat.

10:31.160 --> 10:32.920
I called Chen Lin,

10:33.040 --> 10:34.160
but he's not answering.

10:34.160 --> 10:36.079
So I came here myself.

10:47.640 --> 10:49.240
You really don't need to refuse

10:49.520 --> 10:50.439
