10:56.799 --> 10:57.880
without help.

11:00.520 --> 11:02.000
It's not like that.

11:03.559 --> 11:05.640
I just want to prove to myself

11:07.880 --> 11:10.199
that I can live the life I want

11:11.079 --> 11:12.760
without relying on your resources.

11:15.920 --> 11:17.959
So if you truly care about me,

11:18.199 --> 11:20.920
don't make me lose that faith, okay?

11:23.240 --> 11:25.479
But I drove for you

11:25.839 --> 11:27.120
and helped you move goods.

11:27.719 --> 11:28.920
That's not money power, right?

11:29.839 --> 11:31.679
If you really mind it,

11:32.120 --> 11:33.520
maybe give me a little reward.

11:43.479 --> 11:45.719
Actually, I know why you're
working so hard now.

11:48.520 --> 11:51.000
I used to be too arrogant.

11:52.439 --> 11:54.360
I underestimated your value.

11:56.319 --> 11:57.520
But I truly hope

11:59.000 --> 12:00.040
you can live more easily

12:00.799 --> 12:02.599
and happily.

12:11.559 --> 12:13.120
Now that I'm being true to myself,

12:14.000 --> 12:17.079
I'm much happier than before.

12:20.319 --> 12:21.079
Besides,

12:21.400 --> 12:23.479
