12:24.120 --> 12:25.799
But if the outcome brings joy,

12:26.799 --> 12:28.400
a little hardship doesn't matter.

12:30.880 --> 12:31.640
You have me.

12:35.319 --> 12:36.599
You don't understand.

12:36.959 --> 12:37.880
What I want to say is

12:38.520 --> 12:42.959
I want my happiness to come from myself.

12:48.400 --> 12:50.040
I believe you will.

12:52.640 --> 12:53.280
I will.

12:55.000 --> 12:55.920
I definitely will.

12:57.880 --> 12:58.760
Otherwise,

12:58.799 --> 13:00.120
