13:42.360 --> 13:45.040
What he said isn't all wrong.

13:48.439 --> 13:49.640
But I chose your plan.

13:52.760 --> 13:53.479
Smart choice.

13:58.199 --> 13:59.520
So I want to tell you,

13:59.599 --> 14:01.240
Jiang Liang is now my investor.

14:02.199 --> 14:04.000
Don't go head-to-head with him.

14:06.224 --> 14:06.920
Fine.

14:10.280 --> 14:11.479
Sir, keep going.

14:32.120 --> 14:33.360
I've reviewed the contract.

14:33.439 --> 14:34.319
No issues.

15:19.880 --> 15:20.400
Yan.

15:20.559 --> 15:23.040
Once the goods arrive,
the warehouse will unload.

16:34.266 --> 16:36.633
(Yan Studio)

16:38.640 --> 16:40.120
Everyone, great news.

16:41.439 --> 16:43.079
The first batch of our ready-to-wear...

16:47.120 --> 16:48.120
