16:51.679 --> 16:53.640
Post-sales statistics show

16:53.679 --> 16:55.599
our return rate is extremely low.

16:55.959 --> 16:57.360
Customer satisfaction rate

16:57.360 --> 16:59.319
reaches 96.7%.

16:59.319 --> 17:00.634
â™ªSharp tailoringâ™ª

17:01.040 --> 17:02.520
â™ªThe present I wantâ™ª

17:02.520 --> 17:03.599
Let me also announce

17:03.719 --> 17:05.679
that our second batch is launching.

17:05.759 --> 17:06.880
Five designs in total.

17:06.959 --> 17:08.400
If sales go as smoothly

17:08.400 --> 17:09.479
