for batch three.

17:12.640 --> 17:13.160
Qiao Lin.

17:13.560 --> 17:14.479
Tell the factory

17:14.600 --> 17:15.920
to add another production line.

17:16.120 --> 17:16.759
No problem.

17:16.959 --> 17:17.679
Add it!

17:17.679 --> 17:18.999
We are selling well!

17:19.800 --> 17:21.040
By the way, Xiaowan.

17:21.719 --> 17:23.479
Keep developing the online marketing.

17:23.640 --> 17:25.439
We need proper warm-up
for the second batch.

17:25.920 --> 17:26.959
Don't worry, Ms. Xu.

17:27.400 --> 17:27.999
Ms. Xu.

17:27.999 --> 17:30.320
Some beauty brands want
product placements in our videos.

17:30.479 --> 17:32.439
Resource swaps are being finalized.

17:32.600 --> 17:33.120
Good.

17:33.439 --> 17:34.160
Keep with it.

17:34.600 --> 17:37.039
Two of our first-batch designs
sold out fast.

17:37.039 --> 17:38.960
Fans who missed out
are requesting a restocking.

17:40.519 --> 17:41.479
Tally the numbers.

17:41.800 --> 17:43.039
We'll purchase more fabric

17:43.560 --> 17:44.640
and add the production.

17:44.848 --> 17:45.439
Okay.

17:46.400 --> 17:46.920
Yao.

17:47.160 --> 17:48.920
Are the designs
for the fourth batch ready?

17:49.519 --> 17:52.160
I've sent the drawings
to the pattern makers of the factory.

17:52.320 --> 17:53.519
Before starting production,

17:53.519 --> 17:55.400
