17:55.519 --> 17:56.439
Tell me once it's done.

17:56.439 --> 17:56.840
Okay.

17:57.160 --> 17:58.080
Lastly, Meng Zhao.

17:58.640 --> 18:00.479
Stay on after-sales,
and give feedback in time.

18:00.479 --> 18:01.160
Got it, Ms. Xu.

18:01.400 --> 18:01.959
Everyone.

18:02.800 --> 18:04.279
We're now gearing up

18:04.400 --> 18:05.640
for the second batch launch.

18:06.800 --> 18:08.360
Keep the workflow tight.

18:08.519 --> 18:09.320
Keep the momentum.

18:10.120 --> 18:10.640
Let's go!

18:10.999 --> 18:11.840
Let's go!

18:12.160 --> 18:12.679
Let's go!

18:12.719 --> 18:13.239
Let's go!

18:14.479 --> 18:15.360
Okay, let's continue.

18:15.439 --> 18:16.759
This one is good.

18:17.296 --> 18:19.381
(Handwoven Craftsmanship:
Heritage & Innovation)

18:20.560 --> 18:22.704
â™ªYou once shone like the sunâ™ª

18:22.704 --> 18:25.530
â™ªThe flowers bloomed and witheredâ™ª

