18:41.456 --> 18:44.816
â™ªMy love solidifies into amberâ™ª

18:47.117 --> 18:48.807
â™ªLike fireworks that lovedâ™ª

18:48.807 --> 18:50.645
â™ªRushing toward the starsâ™ª

18:50.645 --> 18:53.055
â™ªUndaunted by painâ™ª

18:53.055 --> 18:55.559
â™ªFearless of flamesâ™ª

18:55.559 --> 18:59.376
â™ªEven if it's just a fleeting sparkleâ™ª

19:00.020 --> 19:02.224
â™ªWe shed tearsâ™ª

