19:45.039 --> 19:45.640
Yan!

19:45.840 --> 19:46.920
We've got trouble!

19:51.880 --> 19:52.840
Why does it look exactly

19:52.840 --> 19:54.160
like our second-batch pieces?

19:54.279 --> 19:56.239
Yes. I found it on a shopping site,

19:56.320 --> 19:57.679
saying it's from the same factory.

19:57.999 --> 19:59.279
They look the same.

19:59.279 --> 20:01.320
But look closely,
the fabrics are totally different.

20:01.320 --> 20:02.479
You noticed it, right?

20:02.880 --> 20:04.439
They are machine-made,

20:04.719 --> 20:05.999
but our products are handmade.

20:06.239 --> 20:08.160
We price at 3,999 yuan.

20:08.199 --> 20:09.840
They sell at 399 yuan.

20:09.880 --> 20:10.999
Within just one day,

20:10.999 --> 20:11.999
they've sold hundreds.

20:12.039 --> 20:13.439
We only released 100 units total.

20:13.880 --> 20:14.840
This one's even cheaper.

20:14.840 --> 20:16.199
Only costs 199 yuan.

20:18.679 --> 20:19.519
What's the feedback?

20:19.600 --> 20:21.439
Some influencer made a hit piece,
smearing us.

20:21.439 --> 20:22.199
A popular one.

20:22.239 --> 20:22.840
(Hi, everyone.)

20:23.120 --> 20:24.080
(To be honest,)

20:24.160 --> 20:25.039
(I consider myself)

20:25.039 --> 20:26.640
(half a fan of Yan Studio.)

20:26.800 --> 20:27.880
(I'm excited.)

20:28.199 --> 20:28.840
(I believe)

20:28.840 --> 20:30.840
(their 3,999 piece must be better)

20:30.999 --> 20:31.840
(than the 399 one)

20:31.840 --> 20:33.880
(I bought online.)

20:34.199 --> 20:34.999
(Okay, now,)

20:34.999 --> 20:36.880
(I'll do an unboxing video.)

20:38.320 --> 20:39.519
Similar posts and videos

20:39.519 --> 20:41.120
have appeared online.

20:41.719 --> 20:43.519
What's with this blurry footage?

20:43.560 --> 20:44.959
Deliberately blur the details.

20:44.959 --> 20:47.120
Our actual products won't be
of such poor texture.

20:47.239 --> 20:48.959
They are misleading.

20:48.999 --> 20:50.120
There are two possibilities.

20:50.320 --> 20:52.759
Either our designs
got leaked by the factory.

20:52.959 --> 20:55.800
Or someone wants to
deliberately smear us.

20:56.439 --> 20:57.560
Guan has gone to the factory

20:57.560 --> 20:58.560
to investigate.

20:59.880 --> 21:00.840
How are the sales?

21:01.320 --> 21:02.080
Zero orders.

21:02.120 --> 21:02.840
Even worse,

21:02.920 --> 21:04.439
many people are canceling orders.

21:04.479 --> 21:07.199
First-batch buyers want returns.
Some even won't return the goods.

21:07.439 --> 21:08.640
Likely got influenced

21:08.640 --> 21:09.719
by those bad reviews.

21:09.840 --> 21:10.920
Now our mini-program store

21:10.920 --> 21:12.880
and video channels are
flooded with bad ratings.

21:14.039 --> 21:14.600
Ms. Xu.

21:15.239 --> 21:16.400
We went to the factory.

21:16.519 --> 21:17.968
The designs weren't leaked by them.

21:18.320 --> 21:21.200
Seeing the bad reviews online,
they're worried about the final payment.

21:21.279 --> 21:22.199
For the third batch,

21:22.199 --> 21:24.279
they demand an extra
30% deposit before production.

21:24.279 --> 21:25.519
Ms. Xu, what should we do?

21:34.880 --> 21:36.679
(Look at its pattern and fabric)

21:36.800 --> 21:38.679
(of the 3,999 piece.)

21:38.959 --> 21:40.439
(And of the 399 yuan piece.)

21:40.920 --> 21:42.080
(Look at their knot buttons)

21:42.080 --> 21:43.160
(and technique used.)

21:43.536 --> 21:44.120
(See?)

21:44.120 --> 21:44.759
(Do you see?)

21:44.800 --> 21:45.600
(They're identical.)

21:45.920 --> 21:47.479
(And the patterns,)

21:47.920 --> 21:48.920
(the texture,)

21:48.959 --> 21:50.679
(and the fabric quality.)

21:52.800 --> 21:54.160
(They're exactly the same!)

21:54.479 --> 21:55.239
(Guys.)

21:55.519 --> 21:56.519
(I'm furious.)

21:56.679 --> 21:57.600
(Who can stand this?)

21:57.920 --> 21:58.999
(No conscience at all!)

21:58.999 --> 21:59.640
You're here.

21:59.719 --> 22:00.479
Good.

22:01.920 --> 22:02.800
What's up?

22:04.679 --> 22:05.800
Yan Studio you invested in

22:05.840 --> 22:07.160
is drowning in public criticism.

22:07.959 --> 22:08.959
And you're still so calm?

22:10.120 --> 22:11.640
Prices inflated tenfold.

22:11.920 --> 22:12.920
Tricking customers.

22:13.959 --> 22:15.679
Even Yuanhang is dragged into this.

22:16.600 --> 22:18.719
Terminate the investment right away.

22:20.519 --> 22:22.360
Calm down.

22:22.759 --> 22:25.560
Are you still that
unflappable Ms. Jiang?

22:27.519 --> 22:30.519
When big influencers exposing scams,

22:31.640 --> 22:33.479
consumers will lose their sanity easily.

22:33.800 --> 22:34.600
Once the heat fades,

22:34.600 --> 22:35.840
who will care about the truth?

22:37.320 --> 22:38.479
Yan Studio will be worthless.

22:39.120 --> 22:40.759
Cease collaboration with Yan Studio.

22:41.640 --> 22:42.560
Cut your losses.

22:53.479 --> 22:54.800
Don't worry.

22:55.239 --> 22:56.239
Unexpected issues

22:56.279 --> 22:58.320
always appear in business.

22:59.640 --> 23:01.039
I'll always stand by you

23:01.439 --> 23:02.479
and help you.

23:02.759 --> 23:03.536
Okay?

23:06.560 --> 23:08.400
I just feel sorry.

23:10.759 --> 23:13.120
When Yan Studio started with nothing,

23:14.239 --> 23:15.759
when no one believed in us,

23:17.999 --> 23:18.999
you supported us.

23:20.439 --> 23:22.560
You invested and got us started.

23:23.719 --> 23:24.439
Really, thank you.

23:26.999 --> 23:27.640
So, now,

23:27.640 --> 23:28.920
with this crisis,

23:31.439 --> 23:32.920
I won't dodge responsibility.

23:34.439 --> 23:36.160
Why?

23:37.400 --> 23:38.239
Don't be so gloomy.

23:38.239 --> 23:39.279
I'm here eating,

23:39.279 --> 23:40.560
not blaming.

23:44.840 --> 23:48.039
You might face refunds, returns,

23:48.800 --> 23:50.600
and production issues.

23:50.640 --> 23:51.600
So what?

23:52.840 --> 23:54.080
I've got funds ready.

23:54.800 --> 23:55.759
Cover the deficit first.

23:58.880 --> 24:00.640
I just got Yuanhang's email.

24:04.679 --> 24:07.160
To terminate investment in Yan Studio.

24:09.039 --> 24:12.039
The investment account is frozen too.

24:13.360 --> 24:14.479
- So, Jiang Liang...
- Don't worry.

24:15.959 --> 24:17.279
That's the procedure.

24:19.640 --> 24:22.560
I can use my private funds.

24:23.600 --> 24:24.600
Rest assured.

24:25.239 --> 24:26.920
I will help you.

24:29.560 --> 24:30.120
Thank you.

24:31.199 --> 24:31.759
No need.

24:33.759 --> 24:34.519
Really, thank you.

24:34.560 --> 24:35.320
Don't mention it.

24:35.880 --> 24:37.719
You're willing to help at this moment.

24:39.880 --> 24:40.519
But...

24:42.160 --> 24:43.320
The more you offer,

24:46.896 --> 24:48.368
the more I feel I shouldn't accept.

24:51.560 --> 24:52.439
Don't overthink it.

24:54.199 --> 24:56.239
Yuanhang Group
has already made the decision.

24:57.039 --> 24:58.600
As high-rise,

24:59.840 --> 25:01.160
you can't go against its stance.

25:03.479 --> 25:04.720
I won't

25:06.352 --> 25:07.959
drag you down

25:07.959 --> 25:10.400
just to survive.

25:16.080 --> 25:17.320
We're friends,

25:18.239 --> 25:19.400
but this is business.

25:22.519 --> 25:23.519
They're separate matters.

25:30.320 --> 25:31.039
Besides,

25:34.439 --> 25:35.519
about your suggestion,

25:35.519 --> 25:36.800
I thought it over.

25:37.800 --> 25:39.479
Actually, Shen Haoming was right.

25:41.320 --> 25:42.759
At this stage,

25:42.959 --> 25:45.920
Yan Studio shouldn't tie
ourselves to capital.

25:46.560 --> 25:48.039
We should focus on

25:48.080 --> 25:50.360
building our own IP matrix.

25:51.519 --> 25:52.199
I admit

25:54.279 --> 25:56.320
regarding Yan Studio's development,

25:56.320 --> 25:59.160
his proposal was slightly better.

26:12.600 --> 26:14.759
But I think this crisis

26:16.600 --> 26:17.600
is not totally bad.

26:18.800 --> 26:20.320
At least I know

26:20.479 --> 26:22.239
I've got you, such a great investor,

26:22.800 --> 26:26.479
such a loyal friend.

26:33.880 --> 26:34.800
If that's the case,

26:34.800 --> 26:35.800
I won't push.

26:38.080 --> 26:39.199
I respect your decision,

26:40.679 --> 26:42.160
and Yuanhang's decision too.

26:44.279 --> 26:47.759
The investment funds
are just frozen for now.

26:48.560 --> 26:49.959
After the crisis passes,

26:50.199 --> 26:51.160
I'll convince my sister.

26:52.759 --> 26:54.759
The investor spot must still be mine.

26:55.279 --> 26:55.959
No problem.

26:56.479 --> 26:57.039
You promise?

26:57.239 --> 26:57.840
I promise.

26:58.560 --> 26:59.080
Additionally,

27:00.360 --> 27:02.320
let me handle public relations.

27:02.320 --> 27:03.199
My network's wider.

27:04.959 --> 27:05.560
Thanks.

27:18.999 --> 27:20.120
Actually, I quite envy you.

27:22.560 --> 27:23.479
Envy me for what?

27:25.840 --> 27:26.959
For having a great investor

27:26.959 --> 27:29.080
who's got your back,

27:29.479 --> 27:32.719
also an extraordinary friend like me.

27:33.800 --> 27:35.239
How did you get so lucky?

27:35.400 --> 27:37.320
Because I'm outstanding enough

27:37.959 --> 27:40.880
to attract a great investor.

27:40.999 --> 27:42.039
Like attracts like.

27:44.640 --> 27:45.360
Right.

27:51.120 --> 27:51.759
Honestly,

27:53.959 --> 27:57.959
you are the strongest girl
I've ever met.

28:03.880 --> 28:04.439
Okay.

28:05.320 --> 28:06.999
I'm serious.

28:08.519 --> 28:09.160
I believe you.

28:21.640 --> 28:22.256
Everyone.

28:23.400 --> 28:24.600
Cheer up.

28:26.120 --> 28:27.600
We must face challenges head-on.

28:27.880 --> 28:29.360
Every fashion brand

28:29.360 --> 28:30.400
encounters these issues.

28:31.199 --> 28:32.160
Nothing is impossible.

28:32.439 --> 28:33.719
Results come from action.

28:36.144 --> 28:36.719
Okay.

28:36.959 --> 28:37.679
All departments,

28:37.679 --> 28:38.959
report your current issues

28:39.400 --> 28:41.039
for discussion, okay?

28:41.360 --> 28:42.880
About the no-reason refund requests,

28:42.880 --> 28:43.479
what to do?

28:43.640 --> 28:44.800
If the clothes were bought

28:44.800 --> 28:46.160
through official channels,

28:46.439 --> 28:47.400
refund them all.

28:47.560 --> 28:48.600
We'll cover shipping.

28:49.400 --> 28:50.519
Any pressure on finance?

28:50.679 --> 28:51.640
Unconditionally?

28:52.320 --> 28:54.479
The first batch's sales loss
will be huge.

28:54.959 --> 28:55.679
Moreover,

28:55.920 --> 28:58.560
the PR manager of the beauty brand
that reached us

28:58.640 --> 28:59.840
wants to pause collaboration.

29:04.120 --> 29:05.199
Do as they requested.

29:05.560 --> 29:07.199
It's our brand's fault this time.

29:07.719 --> 29:08.920
Comfort customers

29:09.120 --> 29:10.039
and stay in touch.

29:10.640 --> 29:11.400
Got it, Ms. Xu.

29:13.840 --> 29:14.400
Huanhuan.

29:15.999 --> 29:18.160
Pin the after-sales policy

29:18.199 --> 29:19.400
to the top of our store page.

29:20.080 --> 29:21.800
Don't delete comments,
but explain clearly.

29:22.360 --> 29:24.199
Take all questions and criticisms.

29:26.759 --> 29:29.120
For counterfeit shops online,

29:29.160 --> 29:30.199
report them all

29:30.360 --> 29:31.519
and get them taken down fast.

29:31.920 --> 29:32.759
Got it, Yan.

29:38.320 --> 29:38.880
Yao.

29:41.039 --> 29:43.360
There's a problem
with the second batch of designs.

29:43.400 --> 29:45.320
But we can't hold anyone
accountable now.

29:45.719 --> 29:46.479
Qiao Lin told me

29:46.479 --> 29:48.120
the third batch hasn't started.

29:48.479 --> 29:52.160
Can you fix the draft quickly?

29:53.519 --> 29:54.640
Keep your originals safe.

29:55.320 --> 29:56.160
Can you do it?

29:56.439 --> 29:56.959
Yes.

29:57.160 --> 29:57.880
Of course I can.

30:00.999 --> 30:01.560
Yan.

30:01.600 --> 30:03.239
Our funds are extremely tight now.

30:03.239 --> 30:05.719
Should we delay the third batch?

30:05.999 --> 30:06.560
Exactly.

30:06.640 --> 30:07.999
Don't forget the factory wants

30:07.999 --> 30:09.920
30% more deposit before production.

30:09.999 --> 30:10.719
Then pay it.

30:11.360 --> 30:13.039
After Yao finalizes the designs,

30:15.560 --> 30:16.400
start production.

30:19.344 --> 30:21.978
(Disappointing! Regret buying.
Overpriced trash! Yan Studio's doomed.)

30:23.920 --> 30:24.479
Huanhuan.

30:24.959 --> 30:26.279
How's our online reputation?

30:26.560 --> 30:27.600
It's a complete mess.

30:28.624 --> 30:29.360
Alright.

30:29.880 --> 30:30.400
Ms. Xu.

30:31.080 --> 30:31.600
Ms. Xu!

30:32.600 --> 30:33.199
Mr. Zhang.

30:37.320 --> 30:37.880
Ms. Qiao.

30:39.120 --> 30:39.759
Where's Ms. Xu?

30:40.439 --> 30:41.360
She isn't here today.

30:41.400 --> 30:43.199
Any problem? Let's talk inside.

30:43.199 --> 30:43.840
No, no.

30:45.080 --> 30:45.904
Ms. Qiao.

30:46.039 --> 30:46.560
Well,

30:46.880 --> 30:48.160
I've supplied your trims

30:48.199 --> 30:49.719
for a long time.

30:50.400 --> 30:51.840
Never made any mistakes, right?

30:52.400 --> 30:53.039
So,

30:53.199 --> 30:53.999
let's cut the chase.

30:54.360 --> 30:55.959
I'm here today for one thing.

30:56.439 --> 30:58.120
Please settle the payment now.

30:59.719 --> 31:00.439
Mr. Zhang.

31:00.560 --> 31:02.600
The contract said
settlement's at month-end.

31:02.679 --> 31:04.160
It's still more than ten days away.

31:04.479 --> 31:06.239
You can't just show up now

31:06.600 --> 31:07.880
asking for money.

31:08.199 --> 31:10.120
That's not it.

31:10.679 --> 31:12.840
Those fakes are everywhere.

31:13.199 --> 31:15.320
Your second batch
didn't sell at all, right?

31:16.279 --> 31:18.320
I'm afraid by month-end,

31:18.519 --> 31:20.439
your office will be empty.

31:20.759 --> 31:22.479
If this debt dies,

31:22.679 --> 31:24.759
I'm done too. Understand?

31:24.999 --> 31:25.640
Mr. Zhang.

31:25.959 --> 31:27.039
We're just having

31:27.039 --> 31:28.279
a small setback.

31:28.439 --> 31:29.640
Business is running fine.

31:29.679 --> 31:30.999
We won't escape.

31:31.279 --> 31:33.039
If you insist on settling today,

31:33.039 --> 31:34.439
you'll be breaching the contract.

31:34.679 --> 31:35.999
Then we'd have the right

31:35.999 --> 31:36.959
to demand compensation.

31:37.679 --> 31:38.239
Come on.

31:38.840 --> 31:40.519
Don't threaten me with compensation.

31:40.880 --> 31:42.439
Your business is failing.

31:42.920 --> 31:43.840
If you collapse,

31:43.880 --> 31:45.039
I'm not dying with you!

31:45.600 --> 31:48.320
- What are you talking about?
- Watch your mouth.

31:48.320 --> 31:48.920
Nonsense!

31:48.920 --> 31:50.080
What did you say?

31:50.719 --> 31:52.160
You're trying

31:52.239 --> 31:53.479
to bully me, huh?

31:53.999 --> 31:55.199
Let me tell you.

31:55.880 --> 31:57.239
My factory may be small,

31:57.360 --> 31:58.479
but we're not pushovers.

31:58.519 --> 31:59.039
Qiao Lin.

31:59.320 --> 32:00.999
If you don't settle the payment today,

32:01.479 --> 32:03.400
think carefully about the consequences!

32:03.759 --> 32:04.400
Consequences?

32:04.600 --> 32:06.199
Are you threatening us now?

32:06.239 --> 32:08.039
You came demanding money early.

32:08.039 --> 32:09.080
How dare you yell here?

32:09.120 --> 32:09.759
Exactly!

32:09.800 --> 32:10.479
Exactly!

32:11.279 --> 32:12.039
Mr. Zhang.

32:12.320 --> 32:13.880
Our cooperation lasts a long time.

32:13.999 --> 32:15.239
What you're doing now

32:15.239 --> 32:17.039
is kicking us while we're down.

32:17.239 --> 32:17.920
Well then,

32:17.920 --> 32:19.120
I'll be straightforward.

32:19.239 --> 32:20.999
You're not getting paid today.

32:21.120 --> 32:22.519
We'll follow the contract.

32:22.880 --> 32:23.920
Stop causing trouble.

32:23.920 --> 32:24.600
Please leave.

32:25.640 --> 32:26.600
Get out now.

32:26.679 --> 32:27.840
Or we'll call the police!

32:27.840 --> 32:28.479
You...

32:28.560 --> 32:29.640
Are you leaving or not?

32:29.640 --> 32:30.479
Watch it!

32:30.479 --> 32:30.999
Get out!

32:30.999 --> 32:31.800
Please leave.

32:32.640 --> 32:33.160
Go.

32:33.640 --> 32:34.800
So this is your attitude?

32:34.880 --> 32:35.640
Remember.

32:35.880 --> 32:37.479
You'll regret it.

32:37.640 --> 32:38.719
Just wait and see!

32:40.880 --> 32:41.999
Watch your own step!

32:45.439 --> 32:45.959
Lin.

32:46.560 --> 32:48.400
Should we tell Yan about this?

32:50.560 --> 32:51.519
No.

32:51.719 --> 32:53.880
She's being grilled
by the e-commerce platform today.

32:54.120 --> 32:55.400
She's got enough on her plate.

32:55.840 --> 32:56.600
Let's just work.

32:57.279 --> 32:57.880
Back to work.

33:00.640 --> 33:01.279
I know.

33:02.560 --> 33:03.640
About the online mess,

33:03.759 --> 33:04.920
I'll handle it properly.

33:04.999 --> 33:06.519
As stated in the meeting,

33:07.039 --> 33:08.400
if there are any issues,

33:08.640 --> 33:10.360
Yan Studio will bear all consequences.

33:10.360 --> 33:11.320
Don't worry.

33:11.320 --> 33:11.959
Ms. Xu.

33:15.679 --> 33:16.279
Thank you.

33:20.080 --> 33:20.840
Long time no see.

33:24.199 --> 33:24.840
Ms. Xu.

33:26.800 --> 33:28.320
Using traditional crafts

33:28.560 --> 33:29.719
as a brand feature

33:30.199 --> 33:31.439
really gives your brand taste.

33:32.759 --> 33:34.679
Your development pace is impressive.

33:35.160 --> 33:35.800
Congratulations.

33:38.519 --> 33:39.120
Thank you.

33:39.600 --> 33:40.640
But I heard

33:41.439 --> 33:42.880
before the second launch,

33:43.479 --> 33:45.080
you ran into trouble.

33:50.759 --> 33:52.519
I feel indignant for you.

33:54.080 --> 33:56.999
Your hard work gets criticized,

33:57.800 --> 34:00.160
while cheap fakes get praise.

34:00.959 --> 34:02.400
That's unfair.

34:04.600 --> 34:07.239
If stock piles up,

34:07.679 --> 34:08.800
capital chains break,

34:08.920 --> 34:10.039
investors pull out...

34:11.439 --> 34:12.159
Soon,

34:12.680 --> 34:15.400
suppliers will come demanding payments.

34:16.240 --> 34:17.439
How will you handle that?

34:21.680 --> 34:22.280
Honestly,

34:23.360 --> 34:25.999
I don't think this issue that simple.

34:27.559 --> 34:30.320
It's hard to push a startup brand

34:30.320 --> 34:31.880
into this position overnight.

34:32.720 --> 34:34.840
I believe someone's behind it.

34:35.800 --> 34:36.639
Think carefully.

34:37.959 --> 34:39.320
Did you offend anyone?

34:50.079 --> 34:51.959
Is it a kind reminder

34:52.280 --> 34:54.880
or a warning?

34:57.800 --> 34:59.479
You know so much about those fakes.

35:01.360 --> 35:02.159
Were you involved?

35:03.039 --> 35:04.240
Is that why you're here?

35:08.159 --> 35:08.720
Ms. Xu.

35:09.439 --> 35:10.559
Don't make baseless claims.

35:11.079 --> 35:13.920
I'm a fan of yours,
so I care about your situations.

35:14.479 --> 35:15.599
Don't wrong me.

35:17.639 --> 35:18.256
Of course,

35:19.680 --> 35:22.519
I do care whether it's Jinda or Situo

35:24.400 --> 35:26.920
will win the deal with the Russians.

35:27.880 --> 35:28.840
Help me,

35:29.519 --> 35:31.360
and I'll help you.

35:34.840 --> 35:35.360
How?

35:37.439 --> 35:39.920
My proposal at the resort still stands.

35:41.760 --> 35:43.119
If you can publicly announce

35:44.400 --> 35:47.599
you and Mr. Shen are filing for divorce,

35:48.240 --> 35:49.760
I'll solve your urgent problem.

35:50.720 --> 35:51.720
5 million to your account

35:52.200 --> 35:53.400
within an hour.

36:01.840 --> 36:02.559
Not interested.

36:02.959 --> 36:03.760
Is it too little?

36:05.159 --> 36:05.880
Ten million.

36:12.639 --> 36:13.479
Twenty million.

36:18.760 --> 36:19.519
That generous?

36:22.720 --> 36:25.400
Aren't you afraid I'll demand more?

36:26.240 --> 36:27.240
This is the price

36:27.240 --> 36:28.760
for you to betray Mr. Shen.

36:29.999 --> 36:31.320
It's worth it.

36:31.639 --> 36:32.639
I don't think so.

36:34.320 --> 36:35.559
Why would I abandon

36:35.639 --> 36:37.039
Jinda Group's support

36:37.519 --> 36:38.920
for your mere 20 million?

36:40.079 --> 36:40.680
Ms. Xu.

36:41.240 --> 36:42.599
Don't be so stubborn.

36:43.760 --> 36:45.079
Aren't you afraid your trouble

36:45.559 --> 36:47.039
might spiral out of control?

36:51.920 --> 36:54.039
I believe this won't be
my first trouble,

36:55.800 --> 36:57.680
nor will it be the last.

36:57.720 --> 36:58.880
Right, Mr. Steve?

37:02.320 --> 37:03.240
Ms. Xu.

37:03.880 --> 37:04.639
You're young,

37:05.159 --> 37:05.760
beautiful,

37:06.360 --> 37:07.599
decisive and fearless.

37:08.760 --> 37:09.920
However,

37:10.400 --> 37:13.639
overconfidence will bring you trouble.

37:14.639 --> 37:15.559
You're right.

37:17.439 --> 37:18.159
I'll keep that.

37:19.680 --> 37:20.880
If there's nothing else,

37:21.280 --> 37:22.400
I need to get back to work.

37:27.320 --> 37:28.599
You can refuse me.

37:29.439 --> 37:32.559
I will give you time to think.

37:33.639 --> 37:35.280
If you change your mind, come find me.

37:36.360 --> 37:38.959
Many problems really can't be solved

37:39.959 --> 37:40.920
without money.

37:42.880 --> 37:43.400
Good day.

37:49.816 --> 37:51.568
(Review Cat: Yan Studio overprices,
betraying fans' trust)

37:51.568 --> 37:53.222
(Boycott Yan Studio)

37:58.320 --> 37:58.880
Mr. Shen.

37:59.639 --> 38:01.200
This is the Q2 report.

38:04.632 --> 38:05.990
(The worst clothes I've ever bought)

38:08.760 --> 38:11.400
Steve went to Yan Studio today.

38:11.800 --> 38:12.400
Mr. Shen.

38:12.959 --> 38:15.079
Should we help Yan?

38:16.280 --> 38:16.999
Help?

38:18.159 --> 38:19.240
She won't accept it.

38:33.320 --> 38:34.680
I'll call you back later.

38:36.159 --> 38:36.760
You're so busy.

38:37.280 --> 38:38.920
I have something to discuss with you.

38:40.639 --> 38:41.680
Is anything wrong?

38:42.159 --> 38:42.680
No.

38:43.360 --> 38:45.720
I'm here to submit my resignation.

38:48.800 --> 38:49.400
Now?

38:51.240 --> 38:52.599
Let me be frank.

38:53.159 --> 38:55.720
I've found a great job.

38:56.079 --> 38:58.039
The title and salary are perfect.

38:59.200 --> 39:01.880
I'm not coming tomorrow.

39:05.079 --> 39:05.680
Dong.

39:06.639 --> 39:08.320
You're our CFO.

39:09.039 --> 39:12.680
You handle all the accounts.

39:12.800 --> 39:13.360
Yes.

39:13.519 --> 39:15.200
Also, the communication with suppliers.

39:16.240 --> 39:17.479
If you leave tomorrow,

39:18.519 --> 39:19.720
who can take over?

39:21.800 --> 39:22.559
Ms. Xu.

39:22.840 --> 39:24.240
I'm really sorry.

39:24.999 --> 39:26.959
But this opportunity matters too much.

39:27.200 --> 39:30.079
They require me to start right away
or they'll choose someone else.

39:30.639 --> 39:32.280
You know how hard

39:32.360 --> 39:33.320
good jobs are to get.

39:33.760 --> 39:35.559
I don't want to miss this chance.

39:43.039 --> 39:44.360
Do you have any demand

39:46.559 --> 39:47.559
about the current salary?

39:50.760 --> 39:51.320
Ms. Xu.

39:52.320 --> 39:53.959
I know our books better than anyone.

39:55.200 --> 39:56.920
What's the point of asking?

39:57.639 --> 39:59.639
With the remaining funds,

39:59.959 --> 40:00.920
our company

40:01.039 --> 40:02.400
can't even last a month.

40:03.240 --> 40:04.464
Please don't make things hard.

40:04.959 --> 40:05.880
We all know the things.

40:06.240 --> 40:06.999
Just let me go.

40:06.999 --> 40:07.920
I can let you go.

40:09.840 --> 40:10.479
No problem.

40:10.999 --> 40:14.119
But the labor contract states clearly.

40:14.959 --> 40:16.400
Financial positions are special.

40:16.680 --> 40:19.400
Resignation requires one month's notice.

40:19.599 --> 40:21.159
Finish the handover,

40:21.720 --> 40:22.999
and then you can leave.

40:23.840 --> 40:24.559
Understood?

40:28.760 --> 40:29.400
Lin Tao?

40:31.039 --> 40:31.559
Lin.

40:33.880 --> 40:34.999
Why are you here?

40:36.656 --> 40:37.904
Before going back to hometown,

40:38.280 --> 40:39.760
I brought some stuff for you and Yan.

40:40.119 --> 40:42.360
I made a scene at her workplace

40:42.760 --> 40:44.320
but didn't apologize.

40:45.159 --> 40:46.760
Now that I'm leaving Jingzhou,

40:46.999 --> 40:48.119
I wanted to settle this.

40:48.559 --> 40:49.959
Otherwise, I'd feel guilty.

40:50.880 --> 40:52.360
Yan isn't that petty.

40:52.439 --> 40:53.479
She's long forgotten.

40:53.920 --> 40:54.479
Well, Ms. Xu.

40:54.479 --> 40:55.999
Don't go too far.

40:57.720 --> 40:59.200
You only care about your company.

40:59.680 --> 41:01.159
Have you thought how others live?

41:01.479 --> 41:03.999
You want me to stay
till your company shuts down?

41:04.559 --> 41:05.880
At that time,

41:06.519 --> 41:08.039
with a blemished resume,

41:09.280 --> 41:10.599
how can I find a job?

41:10.959 --> 41:12.720
I know labor laws!

41:12.800 --> 41:14.200
I'll pay the penalty.

41:15.056 --> 41:15.888
Well,

41:16.079 --> 41:17.159
wait a moment.

41:17.599 --> 41:19.079
Who are you?

41:19.312 --> 41:20.079
Well,

41:20.559 --> 41:21.760
it doesn't matter.

41:22.400 --> 41:24.039
I heard what you just said.

41:24.680 --> 41:25.920
As CFO,

41:26.320 --> 41:27.599
you must complete

41:27.599 --> 41:29.159
handover procedures before leaving.

41:29.760 --> 41:33.159
You must ensure financial operations'
continuity and stability.

41:33.959 --> 41:35.079
Resigning without handover

41:35.439 --> 41:37.079
may violate financial discipline

41:37.159 --> 41:37.999
and accounting rules.

41:38.680 --> 41:39.400
It's illegal.

41:39.840 --> 41:41.119
You know that, right?

41:42.280 --> 41:42.840
Fine.

41:43.800 --> 41:45.519
I'll hand over this mess.

41:45.999 --> 41:46.720
You dare take it?

41:47.519 --> 41:48.999
Why not?

41:49.599 --> 41:51.240
But don't think leaving

41:51.559 --> 41:53.320
clears you of responsibility.

41:53.880 --> 41:56.559
You must ensure all transferred ledgers,

41:56.599 --> 41:58.360
reports, and related documents

41:58.680 --> 42:00.639
are complete and error-free.

42:00.959 --> 42:04.599
Guarantee the legality and authenticity.

42:04.880 --> 42:06.240
You're legally liable.

42:07.079 --> 42:08.880
If you don't mind me
informing your next boss,

42:09.320 --> 42:10.720
then fine.

42:15.999 --> 42:16.680
Okay.

42:16.840 --> 42:17.720
I'll do the handover.

42:18.639 --> 42:20.039
But let me make it clear.

42:20.760 --> 42:21.519
My time is limited.

42:21.880 --> 42:23.119
I'm giving you just two days.

42:23.439 --> 42:24.079
Ms. Xu.

42:24.519 --> 42:25.720
Find someone experienced

42:25.840 --> 42:27.119
to take over.

42:27.360 --> 42:28.920
I won't wait long.

42:29.039 --> 42:29.840
What a coincidence.

42:31.360 --> 42:32.840
I'm Bachelor in accounting,

42:33.280 --> 42:34.680
Master in finance,

42:35.039 --> 42:36.200
and certified accountant.

42:36.840 --> 42:38.800
You've messed
with the wrong person this time.

42:39.400 --> 42:40.439
Let's start now.

42:40.959 --> 42:42.320
If there's a single slip,

42:42.519 --> 42:43.360
you're not leaving.

42:51.119 --> 42:51.720
Ms. Xu.

42:52.720 --> 42:53.456
Ms. Qiao.

42:53.599 --> 42:54.599
If you trust me,

42:55.119 --> 42:56.599
let me handle the financial handover.

43:00.439 --> 43:01.920
Alright.

43:02.400 --> 43:03.760
The office's on the second floor.

43:05.200 --> 43:05.840
Thank you.

43:07.079 --> 43:07.959
Thanks, Lin Tao.

43:07.999 --> 43:08.559
No problem.

43:12.280 --> 43:12.959
Why is he here?

43:13.519 --> 43:15.959
He said he did something improper,

43:15.959 --> 43:17.159
so he came to apologize.

43:18.479 --> 43:18.999
That's all?

43:51.999 --> 43:52.559
Yao.

43:53.280 --> 43:55.479
Have the journals and ledgers
been sorted out?

43:56.200 --> 43:56.959
Yes.

43:57.200 --> 43:58.360
Here.

44:00.159 --> 44:00.800
Thank you.

44:04.240 --> 44:04.912
Ms. Qiao.

44:05.840 --> 44:06.240
Ms. Qiao.

44:06.840 --> 44:07.920
I made you instant noodles.

44:08.439 --> 44:09.040
Thanks.

44:09.599 --> 44:10.640
How much is left?

44:11.400 --> 44:13.872
When the journals and ledgers all done,
I'll go over it again.

44:14.760 --> 44:15.720
Go home now.

44:15.720 --> 44:16.519
Do it tomorrow.

44:17.439 --> 44:17.999
It's okay.

44:19.119 --> 44:21.039
The books are a mess now.

44:21.639 --> 44:22.959
He's in such a rush to quit,

44:23.320 --> 44:24.360
even willing to pay.

44:24.920 --> 44:26.039
Maybe something's fishy.

44:27.079 --> 44:28.360
Better to clear it up fast.

44:30.800 --> 44:31.639
By the way,

44:32.519 --> 44:34.159
there's something you and Xu Yan

44:34.200 --> 44:35.280
should be aware of.

44:36.360 --> 44:37.920
There is all outflow,

44:38.200 --> 44:39.200
no income this month.

44:39.479 --> 44:41.999
I think one month later...

44:45.280 --> 44:46.159
Alright, I see.

44:47.320 --> 44:48.880
Thank you for your help this time.

44:49.559 --> 44:50.680
No need.

44:51.280 --> 44:52.360
We're all working outside.

44:52.400 --> 44:53.720
Call me if you need anything.

44:53.959 --> 44:54.512
Okay.

44:54.512 --> 44:55.120
Keep it up.

44:55.120 --> 44:55.840
I'm leaving.

44:55.999 --> 44:56.528
Alright.

44:59.959 --> 45:00.639
Mrs. Baraikin.

45:01.079 --> 45:02.320
Satisfied with this room?

45:02.920 --> 45:04.039
Yes.

45:04.479 --> 45:06.280
Mr. Shen, you're so considerate.

45:06.800 --> 45:07.360
Have a seat.

45:07.360 --> 45:08.048
Alright.

45:09.720 --> 45:12.079
Mr. Baraikin and I
feel like old friends.

45:12.280 --> 45:14.880
We agreed if you came to Jingzhou,

45:15.039 --> 45:16.439
I'd treat you well.

45:16.880 --> 45:19.240
Indeed. Today, he was supposed to come

45:19.240 --> 45:20.720
but got assigned other tasks

45:20.720 --> 45:22.280
after landing.

45:22.880 --> 45:23.400
That's okay.

45:24.039 --> 45:26.680
I'll adjust my schedule for him.

45:27.880 --> 45:29.400
By the way, Yan truly misses you.

45:30.840 --> 45:31.400
Where is she?

45:32.079 --> 45:34.479
I planned to bring her here,

45:34.800 --> 45:37.360
but her company ran into some troubles.

45:37.880 --> 45:38.880
So I didn't bring her.

45:39.559 --> 45:40.400
What troubles?

45:40.720 --> 45:41.840
Can I help?

45:41.959 --> 45:43.920
Inform Huanhuan and Meng Zhao.

45:44.360 --> 45:45.840
The online buzz needs control.

45:45.840 --> 45:46.480
Of course.

45:46.680 --> 45:47.360
Ms. Xu.

45:48.200 --> 45:49.280
I've been waiting for you.

45:49.999 --> 45:50.880
Mr. Liu.

45:52.039 --> 45:52.720
Mr. Zhang.

45:53.079 --> 45:53.720
Mr. Zhao.

45:54.479 --> 45:55.479
What brings you here?

45:56.039 --> 45:56.599
Ms. Xu.

45:57.439 --> 45:58.439
Last time when I came,

45:58.639 --> 45:59.320
you weren't here.

45:59.800 --> 46:00.680
Then what?

46:00.920 --> 46:01.760
Your colleague,

46:02.159 --> 46:04.320
Ms. Qiao chased me away.

46:04.920 --> 46:06.999
It wasn't the due date,
but they came for payment.

46:07.039 --> 46:09.639
Let's have some good tea and talk, okay?

46:09.880 --> 46:10.559
This way.

46:13.200 --> 46:14.160
Prepare some great tea.

46:19.999 --> 46:20.760
Ms. Xu.

46:21.599 --> 46:24.039
Last time, Mr. Zhang
came to collect payment,

46:24.599 --> 46:26.439
but your young staff scolded him away.

46:28.439 --> 46:29.119
Rest assured.

46:29.400 --> 46:30.400
we're not here

46:30.519 --> 46:31.479
to cause trouble today.

46:31.639 --> 46:32.159
Look.

46:32.360 --> 46:32.880
Today,

46:33.200 --> 46:34.079
the production team,

46:34.720 --> 46:35.559
material suppliers,

46:35.999 --> 46:37.439
and logistics partners are all here.

46:37.920 --> 46:39.479
We just want to ask

46:39.880 --> 46:42.360
will you still produce the third batch

46:42.720 --> 46:43.959
as plan?

46:44.079 --> 46:45.360
Of course we will.

46:46.559 --> 46:47.360
Mr. Zhang.

46:47.920 --> 46:48.840
I'm sorry

46:49.280 --> 46:50.999
about last time.

46:51.240 --> 46:53.360
We've had a lot on our plate.

46:53.840 --> 46:56.039
We've completed the revised designs

46:56.039 --> 46:56.800
for that batch.

46:57.079 --> 46:58.360
We're re-sampling

46:59.119 --> 47:01.280
and redoing the packaging.

47:02.400 --> 47:03.240
I see.

47:03.840 --> 47:04.479
Well,

47:05.320 --> 47:05.936
okay.

47:06.639 --> 47:07.999
But we have one condition.

47:08.639 --> 47:09.519
For the three sectors

47:10.039 --> 47:11.519
we are handling,

47:11.680 --> 47:13.840
the deposit goes up by 10%.

47:14.680 --> 47:15.920
Right.

47:28.200 --> 47:28.760
Alright.

47:29.800 --> 47:30.320
No problem.

47:31.800 --> 47:32.920
See?

47:33.119 --> 47:34.920
She's got funds.

47:35.880 --> 47:36.639
Ms. Xu.

47:36.760 --> 47:38.519
We know you're married

47:38.639 --> 47:40.079
to Mr. Shen from Jinda Group.

47:40.360 --> 47:42.920
This is pocket change to you.

47:43.599 --> 47:44.959
We're small business owners.

47:45.039 --> 47:46.079
We can't afford delays.

47:46.720 --> 47:47.439
So...

47:47.519 --> 47:49.599
If you want to keep working with us,

47:50.760 --> 47:53.200
pay the final payment

47:53.599 --> 47:54.639
for the second batch too.

47:55.280 --> 47:56.039
Mr. Liu.

47:56.439 --> 47:57.840
The second batch

47:58.280 --> 47:59.680
isn't due yet.

48:00.439 --> 48:04.400
Now our sales have been rough.

48:05.119 --> 48:07.880
Funds are currently tight.

48:08.760 --> 48:09.400
Then...

48:10.720 --> 48:11.999
Ask your husband.

48:12.400 --> 48:14.320
This is nothing

48:14.519 --> 48:15.880
for Jinda Group.

48:18.880 --> 48:21.360
My company has nothing to do
with Jinda Group.

48:27.720 --> 48:28.559
Ms. Xu.

48:29.479 --> 48:30.559
We're all businesspeople.

48:30.800 --> 48:31.760
Business is business.

48:32.959 --> 48:34.280
Given the situation now,

48:34.559 --> 48:35.999
we can't trust you.

48:37.200 --> 48:38.439
No payment today,

48:39.159 --> 48:40.639
we'll terminate the contract.

48:41.559 --> 48:43.039
That's true.

48:43.159 --> 48:44.079
See? I've told you!

48:44.559 --> 48:46.559
They're broke!

48:47.360 --> 48:48.240
Xu Yan,

48:48.840 --> 48:50.559
all your assets

48:50.920 --> 48:52.039
are frozen, right?

48:52.240 --> 48:53.320
Who told you that?

48:53.400 --> 48:54.920
Don't spread rumors, okay?

48:55.920 --> 48:57.200
Me? Spreading rumors?

48:57.400 --> 48:58.840
Everyone has heard.

48:59.200 --> 49:00.360
Go ask anyone.

49:01.320 --> 49:01.880
Exactly.

49:02.280 --> 49:03.280
Empty words won't work.

49:03.599 --> 49:05.079
We want money.

49:05.519 --> 49:07.200
You can't even pay the final payment

49:07.360 --> 49:08.400
but claim you're fine?

49:08.519 --> 49:09.479
Who'd believe that?

49:10.119 --> 49:10.760
Ms. Xu.

49:11.159 --> 49:12.200
I have only one request.

49:12.599 --> 49:15.999
Show us what you've got right now.

49:16.240 --> 49:17.800
And we'll let it go.

49:17.880 --> 49:18.680
No problem.

49:19.400 --> 49:20.599
But I have one condition.

49:21.280 --> 49:22.639
Once you receive the payment,

49:22.880 --> 49:25.240
Yan Studio will permanently
cease cooperation with you.

